{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/react/htmlRendering","webpackCompilationHash":"b202c05f208010a6818f","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"48e4f218-af1c-5187-bcce-37760e9c355f","html":"<span class=\"notice\">\n  <em>TIL 내용이므로 잘못된 내용은 댓글 부탁드립니다</em>\n</span>\n<p>React에서는 cross-site scripting(XSS) 공격을 막기 위해 렌더링 메소드 내부에서 html태그가 담겨 있는 string 형태를 렌더링하면, 태그로 인식이 안되고 문자열 그대로 렌더링되게 된다.</p>\n<p>만약 이런 코드가 있다고 가정해 보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Test</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> codes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;script>console.log('Hello world')&lt;/script>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>codes<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Test<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>결과화면</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/a1b4d/html_rendering_01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.066666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_01\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_01\"\n        src=\"/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/aa03c/html_rendering_01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/31ba1/html_rendering_01.jpg 186w,\n/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/1160a/html_rendering_01.jpg 373w,\n/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/aa03c/html_rendering_01.jpg 745w,\n/static/4d26bd2b8138ca07231954c014d39692/a1b4d/html_rendering_01.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>만약 위 문자열에 태그가 적용된 상태로 렌더링이 된다면, 사용자가 임의로 웹페이지에 스크립트를 먹일 수 있게되어 취약점이 생길 것이다.</p>\n<p>React에선 이 같은 취약점을 차단하기 위해서 텍스트형태로만 렌더링하게 설정되어 있다.</p>\n<p>하지만 dangerouslySetInnerHTML을 속성 값으로 넣어줌으로써 텍스트를 태그로 렌더링 시킬 수 있는데, 이 속성은 직접 HTML을 설정할 수 있지만 위험하다는 것을 상기시키기 위해 키를 사용한다. 이 키를 사용할때는 XSS 공격의 별도의 대비를 하는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<p>사용법은 아래의 코드와 같다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Test</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> codes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;b>Hello world&lt;/b>'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">dangerouslySetInnerHTML</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> __html<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> codes <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Test<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>결과화면</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/a1b4d/html_rendering_02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.066666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_02\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_02\"\n        src=\"/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/aa03c/html_rendering_02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/31ba1/html_rendering_02.jpg 186w,\n/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/1160a/html_rendering_02.jpg 373w,\n/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/aa03c/html_rendering_02.jpg 745w,\n/static/7a90383077f1124f5287599f7b29e086/a1b4d/html_rendering_02.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>다른 상황으로는</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/a1b4d/html_rendering_03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.533333333333335%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_03\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_03\"\n        src=\"/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/aa03c/html_rendering_03.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/31ba1/html_rendering_03.jpg 186w,\n/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/1160a/html_rendering_03.jpg 373w,\n/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/aa03c/html_rendering_03.jpg 745w,\n/static/8e02633e658da03b47dd2bac7ce9ae2c/a1b4d/html_rendering_03.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위와 같이 textarea에 입력된 값이 enter키로 줄바꿈이 있는 댓글이라 가정하고, 해당 등록 버튼을 눌러 textarea의 value 값을 html로 렌더링해보면</p>\n<br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/a1b4d/html_rendering_04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 6.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_04\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_04\"\n        src=\"/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/aa03c/html_rendering_04.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/31ba1/html_rendering_04.jpg 186w,\n/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/1160a/html_rendering_04.jpg 373w,\n/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/aa03c/html_rendering_04.jpg 745w,\n/static/59eeece4429ced9e0a60746107f14bd9/a1b4d/html_rendering_04.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 원하는대로 줄바꿈이 일어나지 않을 것이다. 그래서 생각한게 개행의 의미를 담고 있는 이스케이프 시퀀스 <b>‘\\n’</b>을 <b>&#x3C;br></b>로 변환해주면 되지 않을까? 라는 생각이 든다</p>\n<br>\n<p>일단 변환을 해보자.</p>\n<p>변환을 위해 정규표현식과 String.Prototype.replace 메소드를 사용(replace(/\\n/g, ’&#x3C;br/>’)) 해보았다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/a1b4d/html_rendering_05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 6.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_05\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_05\"\n        src=\"/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/aa03c/html_rendering_05.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/31ba1/html_rendering_05.jpg 186w,\n/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/1160a/html_rendering_05.jpg 373w,\n/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/aa03c/html_rendering_05.jpg 745w,\n/static/a1657ef5b79009730a230febb613eb48/a1b4d/html_rendering_05.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>개행문자가 <b>&#x3C;br></b>로 변환은 되었다. 하지만 문자열로 렌더링되어 그대로 노출된다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>위와 같은 상황에서 위에서 언급했던 dangerouslySetInnerHTML를 사용할 수 있지만 이보다 더 좋은 방법이 있다.\n바로 map을 사용하는 것이다.</p>\n<br>\n<p>개행문자 \\n을 기준으로 문자열을 배열로 나누어보자.<br>\n문자열을 배열로 사용하는 것에는 split을 사용해보자.\n그럼 아까와 같은 문자열이 아래의 배열 처럼 나눠질 것이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/a1b4d/html_rendering_06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.466666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_06\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_06\"\n        src=\"/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/aa03c/html_rendering_06.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/31ba1/html_rendering_06.jpg 186w,\n/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/1160a/html_rendering_06.jpg 373w,\n/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/aa03c/html_rendering_06.jpg 745w,\n/static/d41a7b79cc1b49e1f76017c52a7cbfb9/a1b4d/html_rendering_06.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그럼 위의 배열을 map 함수를 이용해서 랜더링해주자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">split</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'\\n'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">cmt</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>cmt<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>결과화면</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 745px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/a1b4d/html_rendering_07.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.933333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"html_rendering_07\"\n        title=\"html_rendering_07\"\n        src=\"/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/aa03c/html_rendering_07.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/31ba1/html_rendering_07.jpg 186w,\n/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/1160a/html_rendering_07.jpg 373w,\n/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/aa03c/html_rendering_07.jpg 745w,\n/static/a77342e9751626095d303443e0a7761b/a1b4d/html_rendering_07.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"reference-site\">\n<p>  <strong>Reference</strong><br></p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://velopert.com/1896\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">velopert님의 블로그</a></p>\n</div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/react/htmlRendering","tagSlugs":["/tag/react/","/tag/줄바꿈-처리/","/tag/string-to-html/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-12-26","description":"문자열 형태의 html을 렌더링하는 방법에 대해 알아보자","tags":["React","줄바꿈 처리","string to html"],"title":"문자열 형태의 html 렌더링하기","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/react/htmlRendering"}}}